For compiling and installation you need:
- boost libraries (http://www.boost.org/)
- cmake program (http://cmake.org/)
- python libraries (optional, http://python.org/)

Basic installation:
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
$ make
$ make test
$ make install

LD_LIBRARY_PATH must contain path with libtexpp.so